Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Straw Hat, Hajrudin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let go of me, Giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take him to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Luffy! It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No no! Please stop, Zoro-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have our own arrangement!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.14,0:04:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrangement?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you said you had a ship for us at the port\Nbut there are probably too many ships...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look carefully!\NNo one wants to moor their ship in such a dangerous port!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:05:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-The ships are all lined up!\NLook how many there are!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!\NThe others' ships are in the fog five kilometers ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this connecting bridge made by us, the Yontamaria Fleet,\Nand go across the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Connecting bridge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm! It's a bridge on the water,\Nthat's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...connected to our 50 Nitamarias by ropes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I'm still fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it already! I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let go of me! I wanna fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, some other time!\NWe have something to do now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're trying to \Nescape but I won't allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already too late, Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That admiral is serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come! Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! The rubble started moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's following after \NStraw Hat and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How is that, Straw Hat?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although I can't see it,\NI know it's right before your eyes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The dark sky is telling you\Nthat you have nowhere to run.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once you set sail,\Nthis huge rubble cloud will fall on you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the ships will sink.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can't you see?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If by any chance you get away from me,\Nthe Four Emperors will take action.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By taking down Joker,\Nyou'll be targeted for execution.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And your future from now will be hell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.23,0:10:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You had pity for my blindness but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I asked for this.{\i0}
