Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}because I have seen so many things\Nthat I wish I hadn't.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where should we run?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna get defeated by garbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:12:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me at least guide you to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us back Rebecca, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you a hero, Lucy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.51,0:12:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This country has done a lot of harm to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't further her misery!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second, citizens!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Past this point are only criminals!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there! I'll put an end to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta our way, Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll shake off the pirates ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not coming down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}! The people of the town are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.25,0:13:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're running to the port!\NThere are thousands of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?! It's noisy back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the people of Dressrosa!\NWhat do they want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Giant! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give it up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna fight anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't let him get away!\N--We won't forgive you, you damn pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save Rebecca-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll catch you no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.61,0:15:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ships under way!\NLet's chase him out to sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.79,0:15:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are they...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is not a trace of \Nresentment in their voice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.31,0:15:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Lucy! Give us back Rebecca-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everybody!\NI saw Rebecca-{\i1}sama{\i0} at the house on the top of the hill...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with Kyros-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah? But everyone knows that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kyros-{\i1}sama{\i0} gives in, they'll stay together
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because they're actually father and daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All adults have known that \Never since 16 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've known of the family of three,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.74,0:16:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,including Scarlet-{\i1}sama{\i0},\Nliving happily on the top of the hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've known about the true identity of the fairies, too!\NWe've all been watching them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we gotta run faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must help the ones who \Nsaved this country escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we follow Lucy,\NFujitora won't be able to drop the rubble from the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Lucy! Give us back, Rebecca-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, everybody! Go to the east port!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our turn to help the heroes\Nwho saved our country!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go! Keep running!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go! Run and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Can't believe it!\NThere are a whole bunch of people!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're foolishly honest Straw Hat Luffy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess everyone wants to help you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What kind of person are you, really?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.07,0:17:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What color is your hair?\NWhat is the shape of your eyes?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:18:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do you look like?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I hadn't blinded myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet you look kind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what should I do\Nwith the weapon that I raised?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.62,0:18:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All soldiers have retreated!\NBut citizens are running to the port!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Issho-{\i1}san{\i0} doing-{\i1}dara{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long will he keep the rubble in the sky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:18:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:20.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the ship great?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:24.58,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE YONTAMARIA\NTHE FLAGSHIP OF THE YONTAMARIA FLEET
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:22.32,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:24.20,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Hurry up and get on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:26.08,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a state of emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you my ship later!\NYou'll be surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's massive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!\NI have four Giant mercenary friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna pull together all the Giant tribes with them\Neventually
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll revive the Giant Pirates\Nthat once terrorized the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Giant Pirates!\NThose were the glory days of Master Dorry and Brogy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah? You'll be a tough enemy to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:20:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I guess we'll see you \Nagain someday somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go to Elbaph!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Yontamaria Fleet numbers 56 ships!\NI know we can really help you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffyland! We got permission from Chief Tonta!\NLet us join, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Join?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't lose in a fair fight
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.96,0:20:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we can't say we're champions \Nwithout fighting pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Ideo and I joined hands\Nand decided to get out to sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we're with you, too!\NDon't forget about us, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This fool's gonna let \Nme be on board his ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing you a favor\Nso you'd better call me "Captain"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, too!\NDon't forget that I'm more experienced than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I go along with you,\NI'll be the most popular one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys talking about?\NDo whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the fact is we totally hit it off\Nwhile we were staying at the Palace for two days!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain!\NFor your information, we decided the order by lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.88,0:21:02.93,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,SULEIMAN A CLASS-A WAR CRIMINAL\N FROM THE DIAS NAVAL BATTLE
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:06.09,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,First, the Beautiful Pirates, 75 members!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.93,0:21:05.26,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,WHITE HORSE CAVENDISH - THE PIRATE NOBLE
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:09.56,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE BEAUTIFUL PIRATES
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:09.56,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The representative is its \Ncaptain, White Horse Cavendish!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.14,0:21:18.32,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,MAN-EATING BARTOLOMEO\NTHE CAPTAIN OF THE BARTO CLUB
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:18.32,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, the Barto Club, 56 members!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:24.24,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain is Man-Eating Bartolomeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:29.83,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,DON SAI - THE 13TH LEADER \NOF THE HAPPOSUI ARMY
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:29.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The Happosui Army, about 1000 members!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:35.62,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE HAPPOSUI ARMY
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.41,0:21:33.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The 13th leader is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.46,0:21:35.62,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,...Don Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:42.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,--Not bad.\N--Honey! You look great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.42,0:21:43.72,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I just said "Honey"...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:46.64,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,BLUE GILLY - A LONGLEG JIAOKUNGDO MARTIAL ARTIST\NIDEO - A LONGARM XXX RANK BOXER
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.68,0:21:49.76,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The XXX Gym Fighting Alliance, four members!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.64,0:21:49.76,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,BLUE GILLY - A LONGLEG JIAOKUNGDO MARTIAL ARTIST\NIDEO - A LONGARM XXX RANK BOXER\NABDULLAH AND JEET - FORMER BOUNTY HUNTERS
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.76,0:21:53.68,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE XXX GYM FIGHTING ALLIANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:54.77,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The representative is \N"Destruction Cannon" Ideo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.02,0:22:01.15,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,LEO - FROM THE DWARF TRIBE (TONTATTAS)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.44,0:22:01.15,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tontatta's Tonta Corps, 200 members!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:05.40,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE TONTA CORPS
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.44,0:22:05.40,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The leader is Leo the Warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.57,0:22:14.08,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,HAJRUDIN - A PIRATE MERCENARY
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.83,0:22:14.08,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Just five members now! \NThe future Giant Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.08,0:22:18.71,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE GIANT PIRATES
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.96,0:22:18.71,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain is Hajrudin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.05,0:22:23.76,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.05,0:22:27.80,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,ORLUMBUS - THE SURMOUNTER
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.76,0:22:27.80,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,...the commodore of the Yontamaria \NFleet, 4,300 members!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.80,0:22:32.76,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE YONTAMARIA FLEET
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.18,0:22:34.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Adventuring Pioneer" - Orlumbus!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.77,0:22:38.94,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.06,0:22:42.11,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,A big troop of 5,600 people in total!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.11,0:22:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!\NWill you exchange cups of {\i1}sake{\i0} as father and sons...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.57,0:22:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with us seven representatives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.82,0:22:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father and sons?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.32,0:22:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! You'll be the boss\N and we'll be your followers!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.41,0:23:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you take us under the umbrella of\Nthe Straw Hat Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:27.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the tough Colosseum \Nwarriors now overcame
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.34,0:23:29.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,the deadly battle against \NDoflamingo together!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.81,0:23:32.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When the seven formidable \Nand extraordinary men,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.09,0:23:34.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,all of them troublemakers, \Ncombine their hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.05,0:23:36.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and raise their sake cups \Nto their big boss Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.35,0:23:39.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,an unbreakable bond that will \Ngo down in history is built!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.00,0:23:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"Sons' Cups! Straw Hat Fleet is Formed!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.75,0:23:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.05,0:23:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.05,0:23:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
